We Automation House is an associate company of SINETEC AUTOMATION.
We are Automation /1 with complete range of Industrial Automation products under one roof. We have a very wide range of AC Drives, AC Servo systems, PLC's, HMI, Encoder, Temperature Controller, Timer, Industrial sensors & Compact Geared Motor and many other Industrial Automation products. Our main aim is to provide our customer, the reliable, efficient and cost-effective Industrial Automation Solutions through the latest technology.
Our team consists of professionals from different technical fields which enable us to understand our clients need in every possible angle. The technical expertise, vitality and innovativeness of our young working team, coupled with professionalism, knowledge and years of accumulated experience allows us to provide our clients most possible service.
We are committed to Industrial Automation with our technical experience and fulfill the relevant norms and guide lines of industry.